history-70-1492%2F&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AThe+Chosen+Few+%28book%29\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Ackerman-Lieberman-4\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-Ackerman-Lieberman_4-0\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><cite class=\"citation journal\">Ackerman-Lieberman, Phillip (March 2013). \"The Chosen Few: How Education Shaped Jewish History, 70 \u08d3 1492\". <i>The Journal of Economic History</i>. <b>73</b> (1): 310\u2013311. <a href=\"/wiki/Digital_object_identifier\" title=\"Digital object identifier\">doi</a>:<a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"//doi.org/10.1017/S0022050713000259\">10.1017/S0022050713000259</a>.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.jtitle=The+Journal+of+Economic+History&amp;rft.atitle=The+Chosen+Few%3A+How+Education+Shaped+Jewish+History%2C+70+%E0%A3%93+1492&amp;rft.volume=73&amp;rft.issue=1&amp;rft.pages=310-311&amp;rft.date=2013-03&amp;rft_id=info%3Adoi%2F10.1017%2FS0022050713000259&amp;rft.aulast=Ackerman-Lieberman&amp;rft.aufirst=Phillip&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AThe+Chosen+Few+%28book%29\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Chazan-5\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-Chazan_5-0\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><cite class=\"citation journal\">Chazan, Robert (2014). <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://ahr.oxfordjournals.org/content/119/1/229.full\">\"Maristella Botticini and Zvi Eckstein. The Chosen Few: How Education Shaped Jewish History, 70\u20131492\"</a>. <i>The American Historical Review</i>. <b>119</b> (1): 229\u2013230. <a href=\"/wiki/Digital_object_identifier\" title=\"Digital object identifier\">doi</a>:<a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"//doi.org/10.1093/ahr/119.1.229\">10.1093/ahr/119.1.229</a>.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.jtitle=The+American+Historical+Review&amp;rft.atitle=Maristella+Botticini+and+Zvi+Eckstein.+The+Chosen+Few%3A+How+Education+Shaped+Jewish+History%2C+70%E2%80%931492&amp;rft.volume=119&amp;rft.issue=1&amp;rft.pages=229-230&amp;rft.date=2014&amp;rft_id=info%3Adoi%2F10.1093%2Fahr%2F119.1.229&amp;rft.aulast=Chazan&amp;rft.aufirst=Robert&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fahr.oxfordjournals.org%2Fcontent%2F119%2F1%2F229.full&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AThe+Chosen+Few+%28book%29\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Appelbaum-6\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-Appelbaum_6-0\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><cite class=\"citation journal\">Appelbaum, Paul (May\u2013June 2014). <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.councilforresponsiblegenetics.org/genewatch/GeneWatchPage.aspx?pageId=530\">\"Troublesome Indeed: Jews, Genes and Intelligence\"</a>. <i>GeneWatch</i>. <b>27</b> (2)<span class=\"reference-accessdate\">. Retrieved <span class=\"nowrap\">12 March</span> 2015</span>.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.jtitle=GeneWatch&amp;rft.atitle=Troublesome+Indeed%3A+Jews%2C+Genes+and+Intelligence&amp;rft.volume=27&amp;rft.issue=2&amp;rft.date=2014-05%2F2014-06&amp;rft.aulast=Appelbaum&amp;rft.aufirst=Paul&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.councilforresponsiblegenetics.org%2Fgenewatch%2FGeneWatchPage.aspx%3FpageId%3D530&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AThe+Chosen+Few+%28book%29\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span></span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"External_links\">External links</span><span class=\"mw-editsect